itude of the Higgs field determines the pseudogap, the reconstruction of\nthe Fermi surface, and the Ising-nematic order. Finally, we discuss the route\nto the large Fermi surface Fermi liquid via the critical point where the Higgs\ncondensate and Ising nematic order vanish, and the application of Higgs\ncriticality to the strange metal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 May 2016 20:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Jun 2016 03:13:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 17 Jul 2016 13:26:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2016 17:01:42 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2016 01:25:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-24"}
