 conclude that Cyg\nOB2 was most likely born highly substructured and globally unbound, with the\nindividual subgroups born in (or close to) virial equilibrium, and that the OB\nassociation has not experienced significant dynamical evolution since then.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 May 2016 20:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-27"}
