 at a selected distance, the dissipation\ncorresponding to \"pumping\" in and out a local slip in the surface CDW phase of\nNbSe$_2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 May 2016 07:53:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-13"}
