lour, and for [M/H] as a\nfunction of $r-z$ and $W1-W2$ colour. These relations yield $T_{\\rm eff}$ to\n$\\sim$100 K and [M/H] to $\\sim$0.18 dex precision with colours alone, for\n$T_{\\rm eff}$ in the range of 3550-4200 K and [M/H] in the range of $-$0.5-0.2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 May 2016 09:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-27"}
