\nmaximum gradient in the horizontal velocity component which has $2\\sigma$\nspatial fluctuations of $\\approx0.17 H_P$ . The exponentially decaying\ndiffusion CB mixing model with $f = 0.03$ reproduces the spherically-averaged\n3D abundance profiles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 May 2016 11:43:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2016 08:54:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-03"}
